      "content": "I hear how heavy and final this feeling of permanent failure must be, and it makes sense that you feel trapped in this narrative. Sometimes, when the world feels like it has completely collapsed around us, the only way to find any remaining sense of self is to step away from the pressure and let others take care of us. While the debt and reputation are real, your worth is not defined by what you have lost, and there are people who can help you navigate this with compassion.",
