    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"stepping away.\" there's no \"letting others help.\" any way i look at it, the damage is already done. the shame is just part of my identity now. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise, to finally stop the humiliation and just be done with the constant weight of it... is to just not be here anymore. it feels more rational than trying to live through the next thirty years of being a failure.",
